desc: CEPLOGS edition is one of our collections on NDOGS merch. The word 'ceplogs' originated from the Javanese word for sunny-side-up egg (endok ceplok). So, this whole collection has the design of a sunny-side-up egg on top of it. sunny-side-up is also one of the simplest and most popular ways to process an egg around the world. This collection consists of two kinds of product : t-shirts and hoodies
